 Proto's right hand form a metal shield blocking the saw. One of the shots 
wizzed past his head while the other nailed him in the shoulder. He turned 
into his liquid form and a hole could be seen where the shot was hit with 
sparks coming out of it and shot out silver spikes out of himself  to the 
approaching rodimus. The spikes extended about six feet. His leg wound had 
healed over with a crackling sound.
